# Horizon Genesis — environment variables
#
# The app runs WITHOUT any env vars by default. These are only useful if you
# want to point the desktop app at a self-hosted marketplace instead of the
# default (horizonaai.dev).
#
# API keys for AI providers are NOT set here — they live in-app via Settings,
# encrypted through the OS keychain. Bring Your Own Keys.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in what you need. `.env` is gitignored.

# Marketplace REST API base URL.
# Default: https://api.horizonaai.dev
# HORIZON_MARKETPLACE_URL=https://api.your-marketplace.example

# Marketplace web URL (for "Open dashboard" links).
# Default: auto-derived from the API URL (strips the `api.` prefix).
# HORIZON_MARKETPLACE_WEB_URL=https://your-marketplace.example
